 getting the service that does not meet your requirements. After all, 
city is more concerned about safety for all Brooklyn residents and not 
here to meet your budget and appearance requirements.<br>​</font><br><span style="color:rgb(42, 42, 42)">We</span><font color="#2a2a2a"> will address all the defects according to <a href="https://www.sidewalkrepairsbrooklyn.com/nyc-sidewalk-violation-removal-brooklyn-queens-bronx.html">nyc dot</a>
